<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>8 SPEED, 9 SPEED, AND 13 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON SERIES - INSTALL - CLUTCH HOUSING</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="3">
        <title>CLUTCH HOUSING</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Position a new gasket on the housing mounting surface and install the clutch housing on the
                front case, piloting on the six studs on the drive gear bearing cover (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018ce">Figure 416</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13018ce" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13018ce" filename="../figg13/G13018CE.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 415. Install Clutch Housing on Front Case</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install six nuts and tighten to 180 to 190 ft-lbs. (244 to 258 Nm) for cast iron clutch
                housings or 170 to 175 ft-lbs. (230 to 237 Nm) for aluminum clutch housings (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018cf">Figure 417</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13018cf" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13018cf" filename="../figg13/G13018CF.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 416. Install Nuts and Tighten</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the four bolts with lockwashers and tighten to 90 to 100 ft-lbs. (122 to 136 Nm) for
                cast iron clutch housings or 70 to 75 ft-lbs. (95 to 102 Nm) for aluminum clutch housings (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018cg">Figure 418</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13018cg" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13018cg" filename="../figg13/G13018CG.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 417. Install Bolts With Lockwashers and Tighten</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">For models so equipped, install the clutch release mechanism and/or clutch brake assembly.
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
